**6.1 Feedstock Locked Coefficients**

-   EFB: MC 62.5% wb \| Lignin 22% DM \| Protein 4.75% DM \| C:N 60

-   OPDC: MC 70% wb \| Lignin 30.7% DM \| Protein 14.5% DM \| C:N 20 \|
