-   EFB+OPDC 60:40 blend: 8.14% protein \| 25% lignin \| C:N 32

-   POS: MC 82% wb \| Ash 28% DM \| CP 11% DM \| EE 10% DM (range
    5--20%) \| N 1.76% DM \| ADL 7.6% \| ADF 22.1%

-   POS: Fe 3,000--8,000 mg/kg DM \| Daily NPK at 60 TPH: N 102 kg \| P
